headline: Stay connected on the water with quatix 8 Pro nautical smartwatch from Garmin, featuring inReach technology
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) today announced quatix® 8 Pro, the ultimate nautical smartwatch equipped with inReach® technology for two-way satellite and cellular connectivity1 – giving mariners access to text messaging, voice calling, SOS capabilities and more without a cell phone connection. Packed with essential marine features to control the vessel, the watch's enhanced boat mode brings boating apps to the forefront when mariners are out on the water, then hides those features while they're ashore.
